title: SPACIOUS & UPDATED 3/2 POOL HOME NEAR DOWNTOWN FT. LAUDERDALE
posting_body: ['Spacious and Updated 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom plus office POOL home on oversized lot.', 'Sprawling Oak Trees, large yard.', 'Large circular driveway, Indoor Laundry.', 'Screened in patio and pool for bug-free entertaining and a crystal clean pool.', 'Leave all the doors open in the winter to use the patio as living space.', 'Wood burning fire place.', 'Close to everything.', 'Less than 3 miles to the Ocean, 2 miles to Las Olas Night Life Dining and Shopping.', 'Quick access to 95 / 595 for commutes & under 10 minutes to Fort Lauderdale Airport.', 'Lawn-care and Pool Maintenance included!', 'Pet Friendly!', 'Available for annual rental depending on current occupancy.', 'If interested in this property or something similar:', 'CONTACT RENTAL OFFICE', 'TEL:', 'show contact info', 'FEEL FREE TO CALL OR TEXT', 'LOTS OF AVAILABLE PROPERTIES READY TO RENT', 'Information is deemed to be reliable, but is not guaranteed.']
